description.narrative: Despite the challenges posted by COVID-19, all sectors are on track to deliver the key results on high quality data and evidence on the status of children and women, including updating global database of indicators; advancing measurement on existing and emerging priority issues; producing analytical products to support advocacy; and providing support to UNICEF field offices as well as governments. In addition, all sectors have adapted (and continue to adapt) their work plans to produce a range of data and analytical products to support the organization’s response to COVID-19 | Status:On-track | As-of Date:27/03/2022
